messages.speech:
There are a wide variety of services available to support Century College students including:

    Academic Resource Centers: https://www.century.edu/support-services/academic-resource-centers
    Advising and Counseling Center: https://www.century.edu/support-services/advising-counseling
    Career Services: https://www.century.edu/support-services/career-planning/career-services
    Fitness Center: https://www.century.edu/campus-life/campus-recreation/fitness-center
    Health Services: https://www.century.edu/support-services/student-wellness/health-services
    Resource and Support Center: https://www.century.edu/support-services/student-wellness/resource-and-support-center
    Student Parent Center: https://www.century.edu/support-services/student-wellness/student-parent-center

Most services are free to Century College students. Check the links above for the hours of each center. Hours may change in the summer and/or over school breaks.
